welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Lakeside, where the charm of our small town will captivate you. Known for its picturesque lake views and friendly locals, we invite you to explore and immerse yourself in all that our city has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all commercial flights and includes amenities such as restaurants, shops, and lounges.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is exclusively for military personnel and their families, and includes a USO lounge and other military-specific services.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
